msgctxt "#32090"
msgid "When multiple sidecar folders exist for the same tile width (e.g. 320 - 10x10 - 5000 and 320 - 10x10 - 10000), choose which interval to use during playback. Preferred uses the Preview thumbnail interval setting; Shortest uses the smallest interval available."
msgstr "When multiple sidecar folders exist for the same tile width (e.g. 320 - 10x10 - 5000 and 320 - 10x10 - 10000), choose which interval to use during playback. Preferred uses the Preview thumbnail interval setting; Shortest uses the smallest interval available."

